Mohan chairs the team and leads the venture in achieving its raison d'être. A believer of the transformational impact that education can have, Mohan's stated vision is to make quality education accessible, impactful and relevant for all. Before founding Beacon Learning, Mohan had worked with leading private equity and venture capital funds in the Bay area and in his last assignment, was the Managing Director for Tiger Global in India. Mohan is a computer science engineer from IIT Bombay and went on to receive his MS from University of California, Berkeley and MBA from Stanford University's Graduate School of Business.  </p> 
