<p> 
As a visionary who aspires to transform the conventional educational practices and infuse technology into school education, Mr Shantanu Prakash is extremely passionate about improving the “quality of education” and “access to education”, two things, he feels, that are essential to improving the education system in the country. “Before we do anything else, we need to have those kids inside the school,” he says emphatically. His ideas took wings when he got his first opportunity to work closely with the Central Government and the State Governments to set up computer labs in schools. His passion to employ innovative practices in education prompted him to equip private schools, too, with digital education. As an expert in instructional technology, he has worked extensively in the domain of education management, multimedia content and instructional delivery for almost two decades now.<br>
Mr Shantanu Prakash’s entrepreneurial skills have changed the face of Indian education, bringing an altogether new dimension to the conventional teaching–learning process. Educomp boasts of several innovations in educational technology under his leadership. The most recognized ones are smartclassTM, QuestTM, MathguruTM, WIZiQTM, Learn HubTM, LeapTM, and MagickeysTM. Educomp also operates through its various collaterals such as authorGEN, ThreeBriX eServices, Learning.com, USA, AsknLearn and Singapore Learning. </p> 
